title: High school girls cross country: Bierly leads Penns Valley to pair of wins
text:
Published By: Centre Daily Times - Yesterday 
Rebecca Bierly led Penns Valley runners in the top three spots for a pair of wins to close the regular season Thursday, beating Tyrone 20-37...
